--------------------------------------------------
Steps to run the program
--------------------------------------------------

1. Please make sure the dataset and jar files are in the same directory.

2. In the terminal, navigate to the directory, where the jar file is located.

3. Run the following command:
				java -jar DT.jar <traindataset.ext> <testdataset.ext> <column number of the class attribute> <depth>

4. All the arguements are required.

5. Please make sure that there are no column headers in the dataset files.


